Temporal Endpoint Object (Open Payments)

Source: R/S7_backend.R
TemporalOpen.Rd

Temporal Endpoint Object (Open Payments)

Usage

TemporalOpen(
  title = character(0),
  description = character(0),
  contact = character(0),
  rows = integer(0),
  pages = integer(0),
  fields = character(0),
  years = integer(0),
  endpoints = list()
)

Arguments

title

<chr> title

description

<chr> description

contact

<chr> contact name and email address

rows

<int> number of rows

pages

<int> number of pages

fields

<chr> field names

years

<int> years available

endpoints

<data.frame> endpoints

Value

An S7 <TemporalOpen> object.
